  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.58,
      "text": "killing two birds with one stone, screen english time."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.08,
      "end": 5.48,
      "text": "7월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.48,
      "end": 10.94,
      "text": "cute, charming, beautifully animated, monster singer, magic in Paris."
    },
    {
      "start": 11.3,
      "end": 12.66,
      "text": "A monster in Paris."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.82,
      "end": 15.36,
      "text": "하하, 김다경님께서,"
    },
    {
      "start": 15.72,
      "end": 17.44,
      "text": "크쌤, 좋은 아침이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.1,
      "end": 18.66,
      "text": "Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.66,
      "end": 23.78,
      "text": "네, 아, cute, charming, beautifully animated film입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.24,
      "end": 26.16,
      "text": "정말 적절한 묘사였던 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 26.16,
      "end": 27.74,
      "text": "It is a bit charming."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.74,
      "end": 34.14,
      "text": "그나저나 이 영화가 1910년도에 그 파리를 배경으로 한다고 했잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.46,
      "end": 37.42,
      "text": "파리? 언제 파리하고, 언제 파리하고?"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.62,
      "end": 39.78,
      "text": "오늘은 또 파리, 뭐 이렇게 하고 싶네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.88,
      "end": 40.18,
      "text": "파리."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.9,
      "end": 41.46,
      "text": "파리."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.64,
      "end": 44.16,
      "text": "네, 파리를 배경으로 한다고 했는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.28,
      "end": 44.94,
      "text": "둘 다 됐나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.12,
      "end": 45.92,
      "text": "파리, 파리."
    },
    {
      "start": 46.08,
      "end": 46.52,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.1,
      "end": 49.82,
      "text": "갑자기 파리, 파리, 빨리빨리 진행을 해야 될 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.82,
      "end": 50.26,
      "text": "네, 네."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.26,
      "end": 52.42,
      "text": "제가 추측을 하건데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.42,
      "end": 56.88,
      "text": "그 당시에, 그 당시에, the people in Paris were in panic by the Great Flood."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.96,
      "end": 57.84,
      "text": "They were in panic."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.08,
      "end": 61.46,
      "text": "Remember the big flood that was shown in the beginning of this movie?"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.46,
      "end": 62.02,
      "text": "Of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.3,
      "end": 65.42,
      "text": "That was a real-life event that we talked about back in 1910."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.52,
      "end": 65.82,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.82,
      "end": 68.6,
      "text": "And Paris was literally underwater."
    },
    {
      "start": 68.9,
      "end": 69.32,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.62,
      "end": 72.26,
      "text": "So the subways were underwater, the train tracks."
    },
    {
      "start": 72.48,
      "end": 74.32,
      "text": "It was like Venice."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.52,
      "end": 74.76,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.98,
      "end": 78.26,
      "text": "You know, people take boats in the canals in Venice."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.42,
      "end": 78.86,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.96,
      "end": 80.6,
      "text": "This was not natural."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.74,
      "end": 82.9,
      "text": "This was because of the disaster, the flood."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.02,
      "end": 83.28,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.44,
      "end": 85.0,
      "text": "And it lasted for a long time."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.06,
      "end": 86.66,
      "text": "It lasted for like two months."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.66,
      "end": 87.58,
      "text": "More than two months, right."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.62,
      "end": 87.98,
      "text": "Two months."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.98,
      "end": 91.86,
      "text": "Imagine the city of Paris being underwater for two whole months."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.86,
      "end": 96.1,
      "text": "Oh, 지금으로서는 상상하기가 힘든 상황이었을 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.74,
      "end": 100.38,
      "text": "The whole city was flooded for more than two months."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.64,
      "end": 102.68,
      "text": "라는 거는 정말 있을 수가 없는 일이겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.78,
      "end": 104.5,
      "text": "지금으로 생각을 하면."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.66,
      "end": 107.2,
      "text": "So Eiffel Tower, that's a really tall tower."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.36,
      "end": 110.96,
      "text": "So the bottom part of that, just the bottom, was underwater."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.12,
      "end": 111.96,
      "text": "아, 심지어."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.04,
      "end": 113.18,
      "text": "Yeah, it didn't go that high."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.78,
      "end": 114.38,
      "text": "The base."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.58,
      "end": 114.88,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.0,
      "end": 116.56,
      "text": "Anyway, it was a terrible flood."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.56,
      "end": 118.74,
      "text": "And some people died in it."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.06,
      "end": 123.08,
      "text": "And thousands, tens of thousands of people were evacuated from Paris."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.44,
      "end": 125.64,
      "text": "정말 혼돈이었을 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.98,
      "end": 128.18,
      "text": "That's exactly what it looked like in this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.56,
      "end": 129.18,
      "text": "Yeah, panic."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.34,
      "end": 129.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.88,
      "end": 130.34,
      "text": "Confusion."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.54,
      "end": 130.74,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.98,
      "end": 136.06,
      "text": "그런데 이런 장면들이 대부분 그림으로 표현이 된 게 되게 많대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 136.06,
      "end": 139.4,
      "text": "왜냐하면 그 당시에 이제 백 반으로 돌아가면"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.4,
      "end": 141.54,
      "text": "cameras got weren't common things 였잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.72,
      "end": 142.9,
      "text": "Not many cameras."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.9,
      "end": 147.42,
      "text": "네, 그러다 보니까 우리가 이제 파리를 여행을 할 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.42,
      "end": 153.04,
      "text": "이때, 이 당시를 나타내는 postcards라든지 아니면 posters가 되게 많이 있대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.14,
      "end": 154.54,
      "text": "Oh, postcards of the flood."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.66,
      "end": 154.98,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.12,
      "end": 157.2,
      "text": "Is that a happy thing to send to your friend?"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.38,
      "end": 162.54,
      "text": "아, 그거는 아니겠지만 그래도 역사적인 것을 좀 짚어보자는 의미는 있겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.72,
      "end": 165.56,
      "text": "Definitely a very unique perspective of Paris."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.7,
      "end": 167.36,
      "text": "You can never see Paris underwater."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.52,
      "end": 170.4,
      "text": "So it's definitely an interesting scene, I'd say."
    },
    {
      "start": 170.4,
      "end": 174.64,
      "text": "아, 그리고 이렇게 역사적인 사실을 이 시간에 함께 알고"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.64,
      "end": 175.86,
      "text": "나중에 보게 되시면"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.86,
      "end": 178.04,
      "text": "It'll help us understand Paris well."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.38,
      "end": 180.1,
      "text": "And prevent future floods."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.34,
      "end": 180.84,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.84,
      "end": 183.28,
      "text": "There's never been a flood like that, I think, after then."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.34,
      "end": 188.16,
      "text": "So now they know how to drain the water from the Seine Gang."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.36,
      "end": 188.72,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.72,
      "end": 193.06,
      "text": "자, 이제 이 대홍수에 이어서 지금 이 영화 속에서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.06,
      "end": 195.54,
      "text": "플립 몬스터까지 출연을 한 상황이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.04,
      "end": 197.2,
      "text": "오늘도 기대됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.54,
      "end": 198.52,
      "text": "오늘 장면 듣고 오시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.52,
      "end": 201.6,
      "text": "Uh, Commissioner, how do you propose to kill it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.92,
      "end": 202.34,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.48,
      "end": 203.46,
      "text": "With water."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.9,
      "end": 206.62,
      "text": "See, fleas cannot live in water."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.86,
      "end": 209.04,
      "text": "And at the moment, as fate would have it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.28,
      "end": 211.46,
      "text": "Paris is full of water."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.82,
      "end": 215.18,
      "text": "Which is why I have not moved more aggressively to drain the streets."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.66,
      "end": 218.28,
      "text": "Water is my weapon of choice."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.62,
      "end": 221.6,
      "text": "When I find the beast, I will take it and drown it."
    },
    {
      "start": 221.6,
      "end": 224.76,
      "text": "Oh, 이제 the Commissioner 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.92,
      "end": 227.18,
      "text": "May not라는 그 서장이"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.18,
      "end": 228.8,
      "text": "We're starting to move."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.32,
      "end": 231.92,
      "text": "본격적으로 뭔가 일을 행하려고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.16,
      "end": 233.6,
      "text": "He's gonna get that flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.74,
      "end": 235.12,
      "text": "He's gonna kill that flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 235.24,
      "end": 238.42,
      "text": "예, 자, 그 전에 이제 기자회견을 열었는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.32,
      "end": 243.12,
      "text": "보니까 he instigated all the crowd around."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.44,
      "end": 245.96,
      "text": "분위기를 막 부추기는 그런 느낌이 들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.12,
      "end": 247.64,
      "text": "Yeah, he's really riling them up."
    },
    {
      "start": 247.64,
      "end": 251.36,
      "text": "He's making them angry and eager."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.64,
      "end": 253.16,
      "text": "to catch this flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.28,
      "end": 253.56,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.56,
      "end": 254.98,
      "text": "I mean, nobody knows the flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.08,
      "end": 255.52,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.54,
      "end": 257.5,
      "text": "They just have heard bad rumors about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.6,
      "end": 259.46,
      "text": "소문만 들은 사람들인데도"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.46,
      "end": 261.38,
      "text": "이 서장의 연설을 들으면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.38,
      "end": 263.5,
      "text": "굉장히 설득을 당하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.5,
      "end": 266.44,
      "text": "거의 엄청 공감을 하는 것 같은 느낌이 들었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.82,
      "end": 268.86,
      "text": "And actually, this is a great distraction"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.86,
      "end": 272.06,
      "text": "for the mayor, for the people."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.4,
      "end": 275.44,
      "text": "The mayor is using this monster as a distraction"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.44,
      "end": 278.88,
      "text": "because he's not doing a good job of handling this flood."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.04,
      "end": 281.06,
      "text": "So he's like, we're gonna use the water"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.06,
      "end": 282.92,
      "text": "to drown the flea"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.92,
      "end": 285.24,
      "text": "and everybody will get distracted"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.24,
      "end": 286.7,
      "text": "from the main problem,"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.84,
      "end": 288.44,
      "text": "which is Paris is underwater."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.44,
      "end": 290.48,
      "text": "아, 주객 전도가 된 것 같은 사람입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.48,
      "end": 291.28,
      "text": "바로 주객 전도."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.48,
      "end": 291.72,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.12,
      "end": 292.76,
      "text": "속임수."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.02,
      "end": 297.38,
      "text": "나름 이 속임수의 전략을 잘 짜는 사람인 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.06,
      "end": 300.52,
      "text": "그리고 he already knew the monster's weak point."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.86,
      "end": 301.18,
      "text": "Water."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.18,
      "end": 303.76,
      "text": "Yeah, fleas are really hard to kill."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.04,
      "end": 305.38,
      "text": "I know from personal experience,"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.88,
      "end": 309.1,
      "text": "they were on my dog for so many fleas."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.1,
      "end": 309.4,
      "text": "어륵이요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.56,
      "end": 312.28,
      "text": "When I was little, my dog always had fleas."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.44,
      "end": 314.38,
      "text": "And the only way to kill them effectively"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.38,
      "end": 318.04,
      "text": "was to give the dog a really long hot bath"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.04,
      "end": 321.72,
      "text": "and shampoo and that would take care of the fleas."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.9,
      "end": 323.58,
      "text": "그래서 강아지는 좋아했나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.98,
      "end": 325.8,
      "text": "우리 강아지 싫어했어요, 사실."
    },
    {
      "start": 326.1,
      "end": 326.8,
      "text": "목욕 싫어했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 326.94,
      "end": 329.02,
      "text": "아, 미지근한 물도 아니고"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.02,
      "end": 332.92,
      "text": "약간 hot water에다가 오랫동안 불려야지 떨어지는군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.06,
      "end": 335.5,
      "text": "Not too hot, but like pretty hot"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.5,
      "end": 336.86,
      "text": "and then you have to keep scrubbing them"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.86,
      "end": 338.24,
      "text": "with this flea shampoo."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.62,
      "end": 339.66,
      "text": "마사지가 되네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.04,
      "end": 341.86,
      "text": "Yeah, special 벼룩용 샴푸 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.86,
      "end": 344.76,
      "text": "네, 아, 그런 경험이 있으시네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.38,
      "end": 347.36,
      "text": "그럼 일단 표현들 점검을 해볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.42,
      "end": 349.78,
      "text": "As fate would have it."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.94,
      "end": 351.94,
      "text": "As fate would have it."
    },
    {
      "start": 352.1,
      "end": 353.52,
      "text": "라는 표현이 먼저 들렸는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.08,
      "end": 357.74,
      "text": "이게 운 나쁘게도 운명으로 운이 안 좋게도"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.74,
      "end": 360.72,
      "text": "안 됐지만 공교롭게도 라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.78,
      "end": 361.82,
      "text": "엄청 해석이 많네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.22,
      "end": 364.02,
      "text": "네, 다양한 해석을 해드렸어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 364.1,
      "end": 365.4,
      "text": "As fate would have it."
    },
    {
